Loop Different Ingredients for Condition vs Decrement.

This recipe uses different ingredients for loop condition and decrement.

Ingredients.
3 g condition
2 g step
49 g base

Method.
Beat the condition.
Put step into mixing bowl.
Add base to mixing bowl.
Beat the step until beaten.
Put condition into mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
